<div id="Idea_3347"><div id="IdeaScale_IdeaTitle">
<a href="/akira/dtd/3347-4049"><span id="IdeaTitle_3347">To Make FOIA Work, Costs of Non-Disclosure Must Be Greater than Benefits&nbsp;</span></a>
</div>
<table width=@%">  <tr>    <td valign="top"><div id="IdeaScale_IdeaSubTitle"><b><a href="http://opengov.ideascale.com/akira/pmd/5831-4049">Laurence Jarvik</a></b> <span class="IdeaScale_SecondaryText">5 days ago</span></div></td>    <td align="right" valign="top"></td>  </tr></table>
<div id="IdeaScale_IdeaContent">Charge agencies daily substantial penalties for each day past statutory deadlines on FOIA request, this may be done by executive order, I believe. Charges should come from overall budget of agency, not FOIA department. Failure to answer FOIA requests by government officials should also be punished by individual reprimands and other administrative sanctions. These guidelines could be worked out by OPM across all agencies to be fair and reasonable--and to provide reasonable incentives for agencies to disclose whenever possible (rather than deny access, now the CYA default).</div>
<div id="IdeaScale_IdeaFooter"><span style="border-right: 1px solid silver; margin:0 10px 0 0; padding: 0 5px 0 0; color: #666;"><a id="DiscussionTopic_3347" href="javascript:ajaxLink('DiscussionTopicComment_3347', '/akira/discussion.do?mode=comment&dbid=2236&topicID=3347')">Comments (2)</a></span><span id="DiscussionTopicTag_3347"><a href="/akira/ideafactory.do?discussionID=2236">Making Data More Accessible</a>,&nbsp;<a href="/akira/ideafactory.do?mode=tag&tag=foia">foia</a></span></div><div style="margin-top:3px;" id="DiscussionTopicComment_3347"></div>
</div></td>
</tr>
<tr id="row_3344">
<td width="120" align="center" valign="top" style="padding-left:10px;">
<div id="DiscussionTopicVote_3344">
<div id="IdeaScale_Vote" align="center"><div style="padding:3px"><a href="javascript:ajaxInlinePopup('DiscussionTopicVote_3344', '/akira/discussionVote.do?dbid=2236&topicID=3344&vote=1')"><img alt="Vote Up" border="0" style="vertical-align:middle" src="/images/ideascale/vote_up.gif"/>&nbsp;Looks Promising!</a></div><div style="padding:5px;font-size:2em"><a onmouseout="setTimeout('Bubble.hide()', 500)" onmouseover="Bubble.showTip('<div>Idea Created : 5 days ago</div><div>Votes For : 65</div><div>Votes Against : 6</div>', document.getElementById('TopicVote_3344'))" style="text-decoration:none;" id="TopicVote_3344" href="javascript:Bubble.showTip('<div>Idea Created : 5 days ago</div><div>Votes For : 65</div><div>Votes Against : 6</div>', document.getElementById('TopicVote_3344'))">59</a></div><div style="padding:3px"><a href="javascript:ajaxInlinePopup('DiscussionTopicVote_3344', '/akira/discussionVote.do?dbid=2236&topicID=3344&vote=-1')"><img alt="Vote Down" border="0" style="vertical-align:middle" src="/images/ideascale/vote_down.gif"/>&nbsp;I'm Not So Sure...</a></div></div>
