<td valign="top" style="padding-right:30px; padding-left:20px;">
<div id="Idea_2922"><div id="IdeaScale_IdeaTitle">
<a href="/akira/dtd/2922-4049"><span id="IdeaTitle_2922">Make Data Available to the Public&nbsp;</span></a>
</div>
<table width=@%">  <tr>    <td valign="top"><div id="IdeaScale_IdeaSubTitle"><b><a href="http://opengov.ideascale.com/akira/pmd/4165-4049">kevin.aslanian</a></b> <span class="IdeaScale_SecondaryText">8 days ago</span></div></td>    <td align="right" valign="top"></td>  </tr></table>
<div id="IdeaScale_IdeaContent">I have requested TANF data from HHS way back in March. They promised to have it mid April, but that was an unkept promise. FOIA tracking number is 032720092006.<br/><br/>We need data to evaluate the performance of Government and make suggestions, recommendations. The federal government does not like to hear suggestions and recommendations and make sure we cannot float ideas that make sense by withholding information from the public. <br/><br/>NEW PROPOSED RULE: All information received from the States shall be posted on the net as received. Federal agencies often withhold the information before they get permission from the states to release Public Information.  It is public when it leaves the State.</div>
<div id="IdeaScale_IdeaFooter"><span style="border-right: 1px solid silver; margin:0 10px 0 0; padding: 0 5px 0 0; color: #666;"><a id="DiscussionTopic_2922" href="javascript:ajaxLink('DiscussionTopicComment_2922', '/akira/discussion.do?mode=comment&dbid=2236&topicID=2922')">Comments (1)</a></span><span id="DiscussionTopicTag_2922"><a href="/akira/ideafactory.do?discussionID=2236">Making Data More Accessible</a></span></div><div style="margin-top:3px;" id="DiscussionTopicComment_2922"></div>
</div></td>
</tr>
<tr id="row_2907">
<td width="120" align="center" valign="top" style="padding-left:10px;">
<div id="DiscussionTopicVote_2907">
<div id="IdeaScale_Vote" align="center"><div style="padding:3px"><a href="javascript:ajaxInlinePopup('DiscussionTopicVote_2907', '/akira/discussionVote.do?dbid=2236&topicID=2907&vote=1')"><img alt="Vote Up" border="0" style="vertical-align:middle" src="/images/ideascale/vote_up.gif"/>&nbsp;Looks Promising!</a></div><div style="padding:5px;font-size:2em"><a onmouseout="setTimeout('Bubble.hide()', 500)" onmouseover="Bubble.showTip('<div>Idea Created : 8 days ago</div><div>Votes For : 12</div><div>Votes Against : 5</div>', document.getElementById('TopicVote_2907'))" style="text-decoration:none;" id="TopicVote_2907" href="javascript:Bubble.showTip('<div>Idea Created : 8 days ago</div><div>Votes For : 12</div><div>Votes Against : 5</div>', document.getElementById('TopicVote_2907'))">7</a></div><div style="padding:3px"><a href="javascript:ajaxInlinePopup('DiscussionTopicVote_2907', '/akira/discussionVote.do?dbid=2236&topicID=2907&vote=-1')"><img alt="Vote Down" border="0" style="vertical-align:middle" src="/images/ideascale/vote_down.gif"/>&nbsp;I'm Not So Sure...</a></div></div>
